1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:31:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n第二樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住為美國風災祈禱：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「多里安」Dorian <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在美國造成最少4人死亡</span></span>，南、北卡州超過35萬戶停電。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=6dc8461c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&h=d997d1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2019/09/05/b6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04/thumbnail/620x349/8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4/0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbsnews1.cbsistatic.com%2Fhub%2Fi%2Fr%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2Fb6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04%2Fthumbnail%2F620x349%2F8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4%2F0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg&h=6aa446ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國歌(快d聽熟！) 、揮<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國旗！！！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=ab030177\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"}]}